- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper proposes a modified version of the Nesterov's Accelerated Quasi-Newton method for non-convex optimization, which is a topic of interest in numerical analysis.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper evaluates the performance of the proposed algorithm on microwave circuit modelling problems, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the optimization of neural networks, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although the paper does not explicitly mention computer vision, the proposed algorithm can be applied to optimize neural networks for image classification tasks, which falls under the domain of computer vision.
